{"tid":2427308,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[支持本土電影]《夜香．鴛鴦．深水埗》獲香港電影評論學會最佳編劇獎兼推薦電影","createTime":"2021-02-28T16:51:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T16:51:35.000Z","uid":226955,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4c3f3a20bb347afaeec6c43eb8e686d9b74b55c8","tid":2427308,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T16:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e1WqhEe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe1WqhEe.png&h=43c3fb8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n🏆【2020年度香港電影評論學會大獎】🏆<br />\n《夜香．鴛鴦．深水埗》榮獲🏆「最佳編劇」，同時亦被選為五部推薦電影之一。<br />\n<br />\nOur film won the Best Screenplay Award and was named one of five Films of Merit by the Hong Kong Film Critics Society.<br />\n.<br />\n得奬理由撮要：<br />\n✒️最佳編劇：梁銘佳、Kate Reilly<br />\n「表面上零散不相關的單元，實則時地互動，盡展不拘一格的敍事魅力，三個劇情短章自成緊密的「循環線」劇本結構，全面揭示香港代際關係與民族身份間差異的社區面貌，從中尋求不同身份積極溝通的可能。最後一段紀錄形式介入，打破單一戲劇性，以深水埗當下面貌再加一層聯想與辯證。」<br />\n<br />\n🎞推薦電影：《夜香．鴛鴦．深水埗》<br />\n「將本土生活日常與城巿記憶結合，獨立成章的四部短片，脈絡勾連不言而喻。攝影師出身的梁銘佳，夥拍演員Kate Reilly，夫妻檔聯手編導，難得承認原地踏步的困局，拒絕沉溺愁緒，深信微小地道趣味、點滴情感交流，終可匯聚成偉大榮光。」<br />\n.<br />\n決選名單及得獎理由詳見：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.filmcritics.org.hk/node/2841\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.filmcritics.org.hk%2Fnode%2F2841&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3Q%2BoCD4UrwaevtQIqI6x5z0%3D&h=f987113f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.filmcritics.org.hk/node/2841</a><br />\n.<br />\n‼️買飛 Tickets available NOW‼️<br />\nGolden Scene Cinema 高先電影院：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.goldenscene.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.goldenscene.com%2F&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3Q%2BoCD4UrwaevtQIqI6x5z0%3D&h=70308ff1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.goldenscene.com/</a><br />\nBroadway Cinematheque 百老匯電影中心:<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3f4KgYP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3f4KgYP&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3Q%2BoCD4UrwaevtQIqI6x5z0%3D&h=5d70998d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3f4KgYP</a><br />\n.<br />\n最佳編劇 Best Screenplay<br />\n香港電影評論學會<br />\n@hkfilmcritics.society<br />\n<br />\n⿅特丹國際電影節 International Film Festival Rotterdam<br />\n台北⾦⾺影展 Taipei Golden Horse Film Festival<br />\n⾹港亞洲電影節 Hong Kong Asian Film Festival<br />\n.<br />\n全球發行 World Sales @goldenscenehk<br />\n預告片 Official Trailer <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3e2ejQj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3e2ejQj&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3Q%2BoCD4UrwaevtQIqI6x5z0%3D&h=decba60e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3e2ejQj</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://Facebook.com/MemoriesAndDrinks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FFacebook.com%2FMemoriesAndDrinks&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3Q%2BoCD4UrwaevtQIqI6x5z0%3D&h=5e2e3b5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Facebook.com/MemoriesAndDrinks</a><br />\n.<br />\n@broadwaycinematheque @goldenscenecinema<br />\n#goldenscene #broadwaycinematheque<br />\n#夜香鴛鴦深水埗 #MemoriesToChokeOnDrinksToWashThemDown #HKFilmCritics #HKFilm #梁卓美 #MiaMungil #王宗堯 #GregoryWong #顧定軒 #ZenoKoo #林耀聲 #LamYiuSing #林倩同 #LamSingTung #katereilly #Teenageriothk<br />\n#深水埗 #HongKongFilm #shamshuipo #油麻地 #堅尼地城"},{"pid":"bfef65d0bc39501b63bca65bcb69c6fc007a2e8d","tid":2427308,"uid":229502,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T16:52:48.000Z","msg":"之前禁戲院之前睇咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係引到香港人共鳴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />特別一影出去某間鋪出面真係個心震咗一震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f8f19ed8304b91b7de4c5bd9e0ac46f01be6d55","tid":2427308,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bfef65d0bc39501b63bca65bcb69c6fc007a2e8d","tid":2427308,"uid":229502,"like":